    <a href="/artists/john-lennon/facts-age-wife-children-death-parents/" ><div class="img_wrapper"><img
     loading="lazy"
    src="https://imgs.smoothradio.com/images/209602?width=105&amp;crop=1_1&amp;format=webp&amp;signature=ZW5pZy6ev-jfd3csLPUnLDN_bk0="
